Interface Id

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ElasticRequestStatus, Habit, HabitEvent, User

    public interface Id
    Objects that implement this class are able to be uploaded into Elastic Search. Needed because the id used in elastic search is outside of the data we can pass in the body, it must be set in the URL.
